				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\%$$\end{document}% in border regions, while Burstein et al. (2024) uses Nielsen data to show that cross-border shopping can reduce the cost of living by up to 14\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
